icontrol

Class GUI_InterfaceMockup

  • java.lang.Object
    • icontrol.GUI_InterfaceMockup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GUI_Interface

    public class GUI_InterfaceMockup
extends java.lang.Object
implements GUI_Interface
    Mockup View used for JUnit tests. Implements the GUI_Interface which defines all methods that are accessed from the iC-Framework and usually reside in the View class.

    It would be nicer if this class were in the test/ directory, but because the TestMockup (which cannot be moved to the test/ directory but needs to reside in the source directory; see comments there) needs to access this class, it is in the source directory and not in the test directory.

    Version:
    0.1
    Author:
    KPP (Kurt Pernstich: pernstich@alumni.ethz.ch)
